<group> spell_"spell name"
{
icon (string) icon picture, filename with extension
radius (int) maximal distance from source to goal
gridType (enum)
POINT - source only can be target
SQUAD - square around source
CROSS - cross with center at source
STAR - 8-end star
BORDER - only far points can be target
LINE - for coverType only
coverType (enum) see gridType


}